    dc:description "FIGURES 22 – 28. Corethrella alticola Lane, 1939, pupa (22 – 24) and larva (25 – 28). 22. Pupal exuviae, dorsal view. 23. Left respiratory organ. 24. Metathorax and abdomen, tergites to the left, sternites to the right. 25. Right mandible, dorsal view. 26. Larval head capsule, ventral view. 27. Mentum. 28. Siphon, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/241962/files/figure.png" ;
